# ENTITY::GET_ENTITY_ATTACHED_TO

## Summary
Returns the entity index of the entity this entity is attached to (-1 if is not attached)

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **ENTITY_INDEX**
